                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780218-72-off376 t17780218-72-victim750"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                   fourteen pounds of soap, value 6 s. and five pounds weight of starch, value 2 s. the property of the said Thomas
            </rs>, <rs id="t17780218-72-cd377" type="crimeDate">February the 6th</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780218-72-off376 t17780218-72-cd377"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780218-72-person751">
                  THOMAS
                   BRISCALL
               <interp inst="t17780218-72-person751" type="surname" value="BRISCALL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780218-72-person751" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
